ql.set_option('output_dir', output_dir)
ql.set_option('optimize', 'no')
ql.set_option('scheduler', 'ALAP')
ql.set_option('scheduler_uniform', 'yes')
ql.set_option('log_level', 'LOG_DEBUG')
platform = ql.Platform(platform_name, os.path.join(curdir,
    'cc_s5_direct_iq.json'))
p = ql.Program('test_gate_decomposition_builtin_gates', platform, 5, num_cregs)
k = ql.Kernel('kernel_0', platform, 5, num_cregs)
k.gate('cz', [0, 2])
k.gate('cz', [2, 3])
k.gate('cz', [3, 2])
k.gate('cz', [2, 4])
k.gate('cz', [4, 2])
p.add_kernel(k)
p.compile()
